channel.description:
[center]Vistex[/center] [center][img]http://oi43.tinypic.com/fm3st1.jpg[/img][/center] [center][img]http://oi39.tinypic.com/14uideh.jpg[/img][/center] [center] We were in the Development thread before but now we are released and we decided to show you guys all our progress on the server. This server is hosted on VPS, we own a domain, it's totally lag free. We are growing, we have been released for less than 24 hours and we already got players coming in. Forums: [url=http://www.vistexforums.com]www.vistexforums.com[/url] Dev Thread: [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,535399.0.html]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,535399.0.html[/url] Some features:
- 24.7 Uptime - Vote4Points - Auto Donation system - Trading - Webclient - AutoCasting - 100% Private Messaging - x2 Point Weekend - Active helpful staff - 2 Levels of Donator status - Regular updates! - Completely Lag Free! - Summoning - 100% working leeches - Perfect Combat - Working Korasi’s Sword - Multi Barrages - 100% Runescape Hitmarkers - Working weapon specs and effects - Working curses prayer book, including turmoil! - All spell books, Moderns, Ancients and Lunars - All Spirit shields working, Even their affects. - Working Teleblock -All New Items -Many Areas to pk - Staff of light Special
508 Maps: [img]http://oi43.tinypic.com/ml79j7.jpg[/img] Multi Barrage [img]http://oi40.tinypic.com/wcfe68.jpg[/img] Better Chars: [img]http://oi42.tinypic.com/b5jm9x.jpg[/img] Claws: [img]http://oi41.tinypic.com/14mys0n.jpg[/img] Range Hitsplat: [img]http://oi42.tinypic.com/15i3hg5.jpg[/img] Ags Spec: [img]http://oi44.tinypic.com/2cdizp3.jpg[/img] Korasi Spec: [img]http://oi43.tinypic.com/30n7j8h.jpg[/img] Magic Hitsplat: [img]http://oi40.tinypic.com/9h2kh2.jpg[/img] Some Items: [img]http://oi43.tinypic.com/244p14x.jpg[/img] New Right Clicks: [img]http://oi44.tinypic.com/2414ebs.jpg[/img] New prayer Book: [img]http://oi43.tinypic.com/2wod4ro.jpg[/img] New Curses Book: [img]http://oi40.tinypic.com/33a4gvn.jpg[/img] New Emote Tab: [img]http://oi41.tinypic.com/keb67l.jpg[/img] Quest Tab: [img]http://oi43.tinypic.com/dzi801.jpg[/img] Shop: [img]http://i44.tinypic.com/dgm0qu.jpg[/img] GameFreame: [img]http://i41.tinypic.com/73lzzo.png[/img] Char: [img]http://i42.tinypic.com/hrk5rn.png[/img] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E4INZedb7X0[/youtube] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BT8hwX6IuXY[/youtube] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVb_7oH2HtQ&context=C390955eADOEgsToPDskJj6sL1vjvE-_HjfM7GZZO_[/youtube] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cVdygEbBa28&feature=youtu.be[/youtube] [youtube]http://youtu.be/Y3a2veMjJrE[/youtube][/center] Thanks for all the support from the Mopar community, without you we wouldn't be here<3 Credits :D -Me -Stefano -Alex -Liamp -Sanity -Mopar Community
